3454.patternName: You know youre meant for more... but your income still feels capped.
3454.futureSelf: bigger income and bigger impact without burnout.

3591.name: Tiffany
3591.theVersion: The version of you who and because you are the kind of person who gives everything when you are in it, staying in healthcare while feeling trapped is slowly draining your life force... even if the paycheck looks fine on paper..
3591.youreCarrying: You have been carrying the part you do not say out loud is that you are scared you will stay stuck here... working a job you do not love... because it feels like there is no other path that pays the same without years of school..
3591.coreDoubt: Your body wants safety... but your soul wants freedom... so every time money disappears, it confirms the fear that you cannot choose yourself without it costing you everything.
3591.desireExpansion: You want a life where you quit the job without panic... where you get to work with animals or serve the elderly because it feels right... not because it is the only thing left..
3591.patternName: You keep watching money come in... and then slip back out... and it has started to feel like you can never actually get ahead.
3591.futureSelf: And yes... you want the beautiful life too... the lake house, hot tub, gardens, land, vacations, designer, a car that makes you feel proud... because you are done living like joy is irresponsible.

10897.desireExpansion: You want enough money to choose your life freely..
10897.patternName: money to feel solid, predictable, and safe.
10897.futureSelf: grounded wealth, the kind you can breathe in.

1049.name: Yilena
1049.theVersion: The version of you who you crave overflow... not to be flashy... but because you are so done with budgeting your desires and bracing for the next bill that shows up out of nowhere..
1049.youreCarrying: You have been carrying the unspoken truth is that it feels like money avoids you... like you try what works for everyone else and somehow it does not work for you... and it makes you wonder what is wrong with you..
1049.coreDoubt: And underneath the luxury dreams is a deeper fear... that you will pass your money story to your kids... that they will feel the tension, the snapping, the no... and carry it forward.
1049.desireExpansion: You want luxury that feels clean... first class, holidays without calculating, a home with a massive kitchen and garden, wardrobes full of quality... and food shopping without a budget or guilt..
1049.patternName: tired of living in just enough... and then watching the money disappear into finance payments the minute it hits your account.
1049.futureSelf: freedom so real you never have to tolerate people, situations, or winters you hate... and you want enough excess to give back to Cuba and change lives without it costing your own.
